  <brief_title>Ambulatory Oxygen Effects on Muscles in COPD</brief_title>
  <acronym>OM-COPD</acronym>
  <official_title>Can Muscle Dysfunction in COPD be Altered by Oxygenation in Patients With Intermittent Hypoxia on Exertion?</official_title>
